OL,3,CAWE workers vote in favour of strike
OL,4,Caction in row over planned restructure
OL,6,FWorkers at the Atomic Weapons
OL,7,FEstablishment in Berkshire have voted
OL,8,Fto go on strike in a row over plans to
OL,9,Frestructure the business.
OL,11,FThe Prospect Union says 81% of its
OL,12,Fmembers at Aldermaston and Burghfield
OL,13,Fvoted overwhelmingly in favour of
OL,14,Findustrial action over what it
OL,15,Fdescribes as "a litany of errors and
OL,16,Ffailure to consult from senior
OL,17,Fmanagement during a restructure at the
OL,18,Forganisation."
