OL,3,CAWE workers vote in favour of strike
OL,4,Caction in row over planned restructure
OL,6,FThe union says AWE told staff in
OL,7,FNovember it would embark on a
OL,8,Frestructuring programme which could
OL,9,Fpotentially create 800 redundancies.
OL,11,FThe union said the nature and timing
OL,12,Fof the industrial action will be
OL,13,Fannounced "in due course."
OL,15,FMike Clancy, Prospect General
OL,16,FSecretary, said: "Our members are some
OL,17,Fof the most qualified in the country
OL,18,Fand take huge pride in the job they do
OL,19,Fon behalf of the nation.
