OL,6,F"Systematically excluding them from
OL,7,Fany meaningful input into the process
OL,8,Fof reorganisation both fails to take
OL,9,Fadvantage of that wealth of experience
OL,10,Fand causes justified worry about the
OL,11,Fvery future of the organisation.
OL,13,F"It is not too late to avert this
OL,14,Faction and we welcome the movement we
OL,15,Fhave seen from senior management on
OL,16,Fsome of our areas of concern in recent
OL,17,Fdays.
