OL,6,F"We have been clear with management
OL,7,Fthroughout this process about the
OL,8,Fsteps they need to take, and in the
OL,9,Fcoming days we will be looking for
OL,10,Fclear evidence that our reasonable
OL,11,Fasks have been met before making a
OL,12,Fdecision on whether to proceed with
OL,13,Findustrial action."
OL,15,FIn a statement an MOD spokesperson
OL,16,Fsaid: "We are disappointed by of the
OL,17,Fresult of Prospect's ballot and
OL,18,Fcontinue to urge dialogue, meaningful
OL,19,Fconsultation and a constructive
OL,20,Fresolution between AWE and Prospect on
OL,21,Fthe issues raised.
